			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just wanted to ask, does Textual Confirmation for PhpBB allow spaces in the answers from users?
<br />

<br />
For example if i ask:
<br />
What is England's most famous footballer at the moment?
<br />

<br />
Can the answer be:
<br />
David Beckham
<br />

<br />
with a space in it?
<br />

<br />
Sorry if this has been answered elsewhere but i did a search for &quot;spaces&quot; and dind't find any posts.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
