			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I never tested spaces in the answers, but I'm sure Textual Confirmation allows them. Otherwise it's a bug.
<br />

<br />
However, there is a small problem. If the user puts several spaces instead of just one, his answer isn't accepted. Therefore, I don't recommend to use spaces.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
